oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Photograph of a group of soldiers
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of group of six soldiers standing outside buildings in France. On the left is a brick building and in background is a board and batten covered building with a large truck parked near it. A diversity of headgear and leggings are being worn by the group. A note on the reverse identfies 2nd from left as Jessie Owen Rice.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Rice, Jessie Owen
